hopobject.body: I'm on work experience weider ultimate body works exercise machine review Lisa North, the mother of missing 6-year-old Ahlittia North, cries in the arms of her mother, Rene' Johnson, after she says Jefferson Parish authorities have found the body of her daughter in a Harvey trash bin, in Harvey, La., Tuesday, July 16, 2011. Ahlittia disappeared from her apartment late Friday night or early Saturday morning. North's husband Albert Hill said they were told the body was found in a trash bin not far from their apartment.
